name: Dulog Creek
description:
Introduction

Dulog Creek looks like it has 3 raps, the first being over 100 ft. Due to the remote location, it probably isn't worth doing on its own but it could be a fun 2-3 hours distraction during a Rogue River rafting or hiking trip if you bring along the equipment.
